Dotfiles
========

To install:

1. clone - ``git clone https://github.com/W1lkins/dotfiles.git``
2. ``cd dotfiles``
3. ``make``
4. you will be asked for your github username/email and optionally PGP key if $HOME/.gitconfig doesn't exist
5. on macos the script will install Homebrew and some sane defaults (macos folder for details)
6. ``source ~/.zshrc``

To test using Docker:

1. Clone
2. ``make docker``
3. creates alpine container with zsh, vim, git, and tmux
4. optionally ``make test`` will call ``perl -cw bootstrap.pl`` and `shellcheck` on ~/.bin, ~/.config/sh-utils, and ~/.scripts

